PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FSurvivors of abuse at the hands of
OL,7,Fbillionaire Harrods owner Mohamed Al
OL,8,FFayed are calling for a full
OL,9,Ftrafficking investigation to be
OL,10,Flaunched.
OL,12,FMore than 400 allegations of sexual
OL,13,Fmisconduct have been made against Al
OL,14,FFayed, dating between 1977 and 2014.
OL,16,FThese allegations include rape, sexual
OL,17,Fassault, human trafficking, false
OL,18,Fimprisonment, drugging, physical
OL,19,Fviolence and forced abortions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FLawyers representing the Justice for
OL,7,FHarrods Survivors group report that
OL,8,F421 people have come forward about
OL,9,Fabuse that took place at Harrods, the
OL,10,FRitz Hotel Paris, Fulham FC and other
OL,11,Fplaces owned by Al Fayed.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police are
OL,14,Finvestigating 155 victims who
OL,15,Fcontacted them directly, including 21
OL,16,Fwho came forward before Al Fayed's
OL,17,Fdeath in 2023 at the age of 94.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FThe investigation, known as Operation
OL,7,FCornpoppy, is looking at people who
OL,8,Fmay have facilitated or enabled Al
OL,9,FFayed's crimes.
OL,11,FFour people have been questioned to
OL,12,Fdate, 18 months after the
OL,13,Finvestigation opened.
OL,15,FA Met Police spokesperson told the
OL,16,FPress Association the force is
OL,17,Fdetermined to "bring anyone who is
OL,18,Fsuspected to have played a part in
OL,19,FMohamed Al Fayed's offending to
OL,20,Fjustice".
OL,26,@yD@OOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FHowever, a survivor-led collective
OL,7,Fcalled No One Above, founded by
OL,8,Fvictims of abuse at the hands of Al
OL,9,FFayed, are calling for the Met to
OL,10,Fbroaden the scope of its investigation
OL,11,Fand make trafficking the primary focus.
OL,13,FThey argue this would allow the police
OL,14,Fto look at the wider network,
OL,15,Frecruitment chains, financial flows
OL,16,Fand institutional complicity, rather
OL,17,Fthan the cases of individual victims
OL,18,Fand offenders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FSurvivors at No One Above have also
OL,7,Fcalled for the National Crime Agency
OL,8,F(NCA) to set up a joint investigation
OL,9,Fteam (Jit) to run in parallel to the
OL,10,FMet's work and have oversight of it.
OL,12,FThey say this would help uncover the
OL,13,Finternational scope of the trafficking
OL,14,Fring, working in conjunction with
OL,15,Fpolice and prosecutors from countries
OL,16,Foutside the UK where abuse also took
OL,17,Fplace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FIt would also add an extra layer of
OL,7,Faccountability and transparency, which
OL,8,Fthe survivors say is "crucial" given
OL,9,Fconcerns over the Met's own conduct in
OL,10,Fthis case.
OL,12,FJustine, from No One Above, worked at
OL,13,FHarrods for more than three years in
OL,14,Fthe nineties, when she was 22 years
OL,15,Fold, and was trafficked and abused
OL,16,Fduring this time.
OL,26,@pD@VOUpD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FJustine, which is a pseudonym, told
OL,7,FPA: "My experience with Mohamed Al
OL,8,FFayed followed a now familiar pattern
OL,9,Fof selection, isolation, grooming,
OL,10,Fmanipulation, coercion,
OL,11,Ftransportation, abuse, intimidation,
OL,12,Fand then surveillance and threat. It
OL,13,Fwas horrific."
OL,26,@oD@EOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FShe added: "His modus operandi was a
OL,7,Fsystem of walking the floor, which
OL,8,Fmeant he would go out onto the shop
OL,9,Ffloor, flanked by security teams, some
OL,10,Fof whom were uniformed, some of whom
OL,11,Fwere not, and he would walk the floor
OL,12,Fspotting the women that he found
OL,13,Fattractive.
OL,15,F"And then somebody from his team would
OL,16,Ffollow up and invite that young woman
OL,17,Fup to his offices to meet him, and
OL,18,Fthen it would begin."
OL,26,@nD@LOUwD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FJustine said that women were
OL,7,Fintimidated into silence with
OL,8,Fsurveillance and direct threats of
OL,9,Fharm.
OL,11,FShe said: "There were security teams
OL,12,Fwho would threaten people's families,
OL,13,Fthey would follow them outside of the
OL,14,Fworkplace to see who they were
OL,15,Fspeaking to, they would contact them
OL,16,Fin their private homes, and they would
OL,17,Fmake very direct threats of harm or
OL,18,Fruin.
OL,26,@sD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,F"John Macnamara, who was Fayed's
OL,7,Fdirector of security, was an extremely
OL,8,Fscary man, and he was very much the
OL,9,Fhead of all of this."
OL,11,FMr Macnamara died in 2019 at the age
OL,12,Fof 83.
OL,14,FJustine told PA that Al Fayed's crimes
OL,15,Fare being framed as sexual abuse in
OL,16,Fthe workplace perpetrated by one bad
OL,17,Fman, rather than a trafficking
OL,18,Foperation with many enablers and
OL,19,Ffacilitators.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FShe said: "Fayed could not have
OL,7,Fmasterminded this system without many
OL,8,Fhelpers, including security personnel,
OL,9,FHR staff, people in banks authorising
OL,10,Fvast sums of cash for Fayed to give to
OL,11,Fwomen, people who worked at the
OL,12,Fprivate airports ` Fayed had several
OL,13,Fprivate aircraft ` and the people who
OL,14,Fworked in the FBOs."
OL,16,FFixed Term Operators (FBOs) are
OL,17,Fcompanies who manage private aircraft.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FJustine said Fayed used to store his
OL,7,Faircraft at Stansted and Luton
OL,8,Fairports, flying women in and out of
OL,9,Fthese locations.
OL,11,FShe said: "Our passports were taken
OL,12,Ffrom us, we did not go through border
OL,13,Fcontrol.
OL,15,F"There were many people that would
OL,16,Fhave been involved in making that
OL,17,Fpossible."
OL,26,@sD@KOUwD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FJustine went on to say: "Then there
OL,7,Fwere legal teams who were drafting
OL,8,FNDAs (Non-Disclosure Agreements) for
OL,9,Fwomen to sign. There were doctors who
OL,10,Fwere performing medical examinations.
OL,12,F"There were also people within the
OL,13,Fbusiness, who knew what was happening.
OL,14,FIf they weren't directly enabling,
OL,15,Fthey were turning a blind eye and not
OL,16,Fdoing anything about it."
OL,26,@nD@YOUtD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FThere is increasing pressure on the
OL,7,FMet to open a full trafficking
OL,8,Finvestigation, including from the
OL,9,Fformer head of the force's own anti-
OL,10,Ftrafficking unit, Phil Brewer, who
OL,11,Fsaid it would help identify and seize
OL,12,Fevidence that corroborates the stories
OL,13,Fprovided.
OL,15,FInstead, the Met are talking to women
OL,16,Fas "siloed victims", Justine said.
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FShe told PA: "A trafficking
OL,7,Finvestigation would look at all the
OL,8,Fnetworks involved and recognise the
OL,9,Fsystemic nature of the abuse, so the
OL,10,Ffinancial flows would be scrutinised,
OL,11,Fthe medical examinations, the security
OL,12,Fthreats, the bribes, the movement of
OL,13,Fwomen, all the systems that formed the
OL,14,Fweb.
OL,16,F"A trafficking investigation would not
OL,17,Fonly talk to the woman who ended up
OL,18,Fsitting on a plane that belonged to
OL,19,FFayed, they would be looking at all
OL,20,Fthe steps that placed her in that seat.
OL,26,@nD@NOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,F"At the moment, that's not how the
OL,7,Finvestigation is being handled and it
OL,8,Fhas to be.
OL,10,F"Without a trafficking investigation
OL,11,Fand a JIT, the true scale of this
OL,12,Fnetwork isn't going to be seen,
OL,13,Fbecause everything's being drip, drip,
OL,14,Fdrip fed.
OL,16,F"And they're not seizing evidence.
OL,17,FDespite Operation Cornpoppy being
OL,18,Fopened 18 months ago, all they've done
OL,19,Fis question four people. It's just not
OL,20,Fenough."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,FJustine spoke to the police about her
OL,7,Fexperience in 2018 after being in a
OL,8,Fnews story.
OL,10,FShe told PA: "The story and my
OL,11,Freporting, along with others' at the
OL,12,Ftime, just faded away and there was
OL,13,Fabsolutely no follow-up or action
OL,14,Ftaken.
OL,16,F"They've missed many opportunities,
OL,17,Fthe Met, but when I spoke to them in
OL,18,F2018, that was one of the last
OL,19,Fopportunities they had to get Mohamed
OL,20,FAl Fayed while he was alive.
OL,26,@rD@NOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,F"That moment has gone, but there are
OL,7,Fmany, many people still alive and
OL,8,Finstitutions still operating who need
OL,9,Fto be held to account."
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) is looking at how
OL,13,Fhistorical allegations were handled,
OL,14,Fand one currently serving officer and
OL,15,Ffour former officers are being
OL,16,Finvestigated.
OL,18,FA Met Police spokesperson told PA:
OL,19,F"Specialist detectives continue to
OL,20,Flead one of the Met's largest and most
OL,21,Fcomplex investigations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,F"Four suspects have been interviewed
OL,7,Funder caution so far in our
OL,8,Fdetermination to bring anyone who is
OL,9,Fsuspected to have played a part in
OL,10,FMohamed Al Fayed's offending to
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,F"To date, 155 victims have come
OL,14,Fforward and reported allegations of
OL,15,Fsexual assault, rape, sexual
OL,16,Fexploitation and human trafficking.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30520
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780902266
OL,3,CSurvivors of Mohamed Al Fayed abuse
OL,4,Ccall for full trafficking investigation
OL,6,F"Over the past 18 months, officers
OL,7,Fhave taken detailed accounts from
OL,8,Fvictims and witnesses to build a
OL,9,Fcomprehensive picture of the alleged
OL,10,Foffending.
OL,12,F"The victims are at the heart of our
OL,13,Finvestigation, and it remains our
OL,14,Fpriority to communicate with them
OL,15,Fclearly and meaningfully as the
